      <h1 class='title'>Care Homes</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 cc1649-50WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1650ws' title='Col. 1650WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1650WS' name='column_1650ws' href='#column_1650ws' rel='bookmark'>1650WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_7'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-sue-doughty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_7' title='Link to this speech by Ms Sue Doughty' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-sue-doughty" title="Ms Sue Doughty">Sue Doughty</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Deputy Prime Minister how many local authority run care home beds there were in Surrey in each year since 1997. [188169]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_8'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/dr-stephen-ladyman' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_8' title='Link to this speech by Dr Stephen Ladyman' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/dr-stephen-ladyman" title="Dr Stephen Ladyman">Dr. Ladyman</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">I have been asked to reply.</p><p>The table shows the number of local authority staffed care home places in Surrey, as at 31 March for the years 1997 to 2001.</p><p>
          <table>
          <tr>
          <td><span class="italic">Number of local authority staffed care home places in Surrey at</p><p> 31 March, 1997 to 2001</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Rounded numbers</p><p> Number of places</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1997</td>
          <td>1,760</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1998</td>
          <td>970</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1999</td>
          <td>860</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2000</td>
          <td>860</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2001</td>
          <td>520</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><span class="italic">Source:</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>RA.</td>
          </tr>
          </table>
          </p><p>I understand from the chair of the Commission for Social Care Inspection (CSCI) that figures for later years were collected by the National Care Standards Commission, and now CSCI, but comparable details are not available.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
